Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.75,0:00:19.53,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖鬥士星矢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.32,0:00:25.35,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在沒有星光的迷宮裡掙扎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.20,0:00:30.38,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彷徨的少年啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.95,0:00:36.10,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感受靈魂的吶喊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.30,0:00:41.35,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宇宙正在呼喚你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.30,0:00:47.15,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背負傷痕 知曉孤獨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.65,0:00:52.50,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於明白了羈絆的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.65,0:00:55.36,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消除陰翳眼眸中的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.60,0:00:57.99,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不安和困惑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.30,0:01:04.50,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃燒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.87,0:01:08.33,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰士們 站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.50,0:01:11.00,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迎向未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.20,0:01:14.42,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果背負的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:16.35,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠稱為愛的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.43,0:01:19.05,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰士們相互支持
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.20,0:01:21.68,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化為風的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.97,0:01:26.15,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全新的Ω神話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.27,0:01:31.40,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就從現在開始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.60,0:00:21.00,LOGO,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光榮字幕組&galaxy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.16,0:01:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好壯觀！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.76,0:01:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就是五老峰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.37,0:01:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好讓人興奮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.98,0:01:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們再慢慢吞吞的我就丟下你們了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.26,0:01:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這種程度 也能算青銅聖鬥士啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.45,0:01:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.77,0:01:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是叫昴來著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.31,0:02:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 很囂張地說「我要打倒你成為神」的鋼鐵聖鬥士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.06,0:02:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 別看他那個樣子 關鍵時候還是很能幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.71,0:02:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒覺得他只是個自大的小鬼而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.94,0:02:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 昴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.60,0:02:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼那麼幹勁十足啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.41,0:02:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在要去找的那個叫龍峰的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.00,0:02:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那個傳說中的聖鬥士 天龍座紫龍的兒子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.10,0:02:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.21,0:02:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是我們之中 比任何人都更具才能的聖鬥士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.59,0:02:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.72,0:02:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要打倒他 變得更強
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.45,0:02:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？喂！別想那些傻事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.86,0:02:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自銀河飛流而下的廬山大瀑布
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.18,0:02:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將其水流 逆流回天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.30,0:03:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無可替代之物！覺醒吧、龍！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.77,0:03:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親 這對我太困難了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.36,0:03:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我不穿聖衣 就將這廬山大瀑布逆流
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.56,0:03:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍峰 別洩氣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.97,0:03:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有如攀升銀河的龍一般 將這大瀑布逆流回天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.97,0:03:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才是真正的天龍座聖鬥士的證明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.03,0:03:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥明明已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.03,0:03:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.98,0:03:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖鬥士的戰鬥永無止境
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.36,0:03:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了地上的愛與和平而戰鬥的希望的鬥士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.33,0:03:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是聖鬥士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.08,0:03:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往嘉米爾並且修復了聖衣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.31,0:04:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你卻無法穿上聖衣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.82,0:04:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是因為你的內心尚有迷惘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.92,0:04:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提升小宇宙 超越自己的極限之時
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.55,0:04:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就可以再次穿上聖衣了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.18,0:04:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這話我已經聽膩了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.98,0:04:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的體內也有龍在沉睡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.46,0:04:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是以力量改變逆境 不斷攀登高峰的龍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.49,0:04:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喚醒那條龍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.88,0:04:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿 快點來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.06,0:04:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.27,0:04:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.93,0:04:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是女神帕拉斯大人的僕從
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.16,0:04:51.69,remark,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.16,0:04:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奉三級刻鬥士 哈利墨德大人之命而來  
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.82,0:04:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.18,0:04:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此路不通！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.82,0:04:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你們的目標是龍峰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.18,0:04:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 戰鬥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.08,0:05:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧 天馬座
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.84,0:05:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幼獅座
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.21,0:05:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天鷹座
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.02,0:05:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也上了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.10,0:05:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 鋼鐵聖衣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.32,0:06:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.92,0:06:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礙事 給我滾開
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.95,0:06:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼打下去沒完沒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.71,0:06:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍峰…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.07,0:06:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.75,0:06:54.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍峰 你終於平安歸來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.63,0:06:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.56,0:07:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.89,0:07:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍峰 我感覺到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.37,0:07:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那在同黑暗之神阿普斯的戰鬥中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.52,0:07:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精進磨礪 愈發強大的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.04,0:07:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經成長為一名出色的聖鬥士了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.14,0:07:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是依靠父親的教誨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.96,0:07:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才能通過一場又一場戰鬥的考驗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.31,0:07:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我的戰鬥已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.52,0:07:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這天龍座聖衣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.15,0:07:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也應該回到它原來的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.46,0:07:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親您的手中了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.12,0:07:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這聖衣是屬於你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.86,0:07:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要它的時刻也將再次到來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.57,0:07:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論發生什麼 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.77,0:07:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不能讓它離開你的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.14,0:07:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 聖衣已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.35,0:07:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可知這聖衣的由來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.93,0:07:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天龍座聖衣在這大瀑布的最深處
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.64,0:07:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在堪稱永恆的漫長時間裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.52,0:08:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歷經銀河之水的擊打錘煉 最終孕育而生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.92,0:08:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並因此具備了凌駕於鑽石之上的光芒與硬度
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.60,0:08:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若你不將聖衣披掛於身
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.11,0:08:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它將再次在大瀑布深處
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.68,0:08:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陷入長久的沉睡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.81,0:08:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 只要你不斷提升自己的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.09,0:08:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖衣也定會回應你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.39,0:08:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 龍峰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.34,0:08:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.70,0:08:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本以為 回到五老峰就能與父親母親 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.38,0:08:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一家三口過上幸福的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.13,0:08:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是父親他卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.08,0:08:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親您又是怎麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.71,0:08:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.93,0:08:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我出生之前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.59,0:08:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親就以聖鬥士的身份不斷戰鬥著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.04,0:08:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拋下母親 冒著生命危險投身戰場
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.72,0:08:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且身受重傷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.00,0:09:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面對這一切 您真的能夠坦然以對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.30,0:09:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這就是 聖鬥士的宿命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.54,0:09:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你父親他擁有許多夥伴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.24,0:09:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了同伴 他不惜身負重傷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.43,0:09:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奮不顧身地投入戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.13,0:09:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天龍座聖衣 可是你父親與同伴們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.74,0:09:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賭上性命並肩作戰的證明啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.80,0:09:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍峰 你也曾與無可取代的同伴們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.94,0:09:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並肩戰鬥過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.15,0:09:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍峰…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.05,0:09:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親 還是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.34,0:09:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.18,0:10:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.22,0:10:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少 讓我稍事休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.93,0:10:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 敵人可不會等著你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.80,0:10:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.64,0:10:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗之神阿普斯已經消亡了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.11,0:10:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人已經不存在了不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.31,0:10:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管再怎麼修煉 也沒有任何意義啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.08,0:10:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親 您聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.73,0:10:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我與同伴們戰鬥至今的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.83,0:10:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是為了父親您
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.79,0:10:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直認為 只要我能夠提升自己的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.42,0:10:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以使五感盡失的父親您恢復原狀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.45,0:10:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 我所期待的生活並不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.55,0:10:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經不想再戰鬥了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.94,0:10:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想和父親母親一起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.79,0:10:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一家三口過上平靜的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.39,0:10:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拋棄它 也就意味著拋棄與同伴之間的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.76,0:10:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你無所謂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.59,0:11:12.41,remark,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺醒吧！龍之聖衣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.92,0:11:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拋棄它 也就意味著拋棄與同伴之間的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.80,0:11:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你無所謂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.83,0:11:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 就因為被無謂的家族之情所絆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.12,0:11:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才一直這麼弱小
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.64,0:11:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.96,0:11:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女神帕拉斯大人的僕從　三級刻鬥士哈利墨德
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.93,0:11:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有我這三節棍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.43,0:11:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刻鬥士？！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.05,0:11:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打倒黑暗之神阿普斯的聖鬥士…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.14,0:11:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的性命 我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.31,0:12:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道父親提到的敵人就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.48,0:12:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解決掉你之後就輪到紫龍了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.77,0:12:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你休想動我父親一根指頭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.27,0:12:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 逞強就只有現在了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.34,0:12:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就讓你這軟骨頭見識一下 什麼是真正的強大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.41,0:12:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有聖衣的聖鬥士 完全不夠看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.42,0:12:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 真無聊 給你個痛快的算了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.31,0:12:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍峰…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.90,0:13:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親 別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.94,0:13:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍峰 你父親讓你拿上這個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.66,0:13:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.37,0:13:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖衣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.10,0:13:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會讓你穿上它的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.49,0:13:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真傻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.28,0:13:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親早就預見新的敵人正在逼近
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.82,0:13:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才硬下心 讓我進行嚴酷的試煉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.05,0:13:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我卻什麼都不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.81,0:13:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍峰…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.93,0:13:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 真礙眼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.84,0:13:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.91,0:13:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是早就說過 你太過天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.61,0:13:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然為家人犧牲自己
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.42,0:13:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想像大爺我一樣變得強大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.32,0:13:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就給我徹底丟掉那種玩意兒 專心戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.10,0:14:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣就能變強了 就像大爺我一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.17,0:14:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我能變強 正是因為有父親母親在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.21,0:14:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才能一路戰勝困難走到今天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.90,0:14:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早說過你那想法太過幼稚了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.62,0:14:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 這種東西 看我廢了它
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.98,0:14:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.46,0:14:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這小子真難纏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.68,0:14:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才不是自己捨棄那聖衣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.40,0:14:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老老實實放棄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.23,0:14:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.88,0:14:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.20,0:14:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是父親傳給我的重要的聖衣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.68,0:14:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我與同伴曾經並肩戰鬥的證明
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.32,0:14:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死也不會交給你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.66,0:14:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 那就去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.93,0:15:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖衣啊 再次賜予我力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.07,0:15:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要守護無可替代的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.13,0:15:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守護父親和母親
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.20,0:15:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此 不惜捨棄生命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.38,0:15:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.15,0:15:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的體內也有龍在沉睡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.94,0:15:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是以力量改變逆境 不斷攀登高峰的龍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.59,0:15:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喚醒那條龍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.04,0:15:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.77,0:15:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使頭破血流 即使身體四分五裂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.32,0:15:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要為重要的人賭上生命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.72,0:15:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是真正的聖鬥士
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.99,0:15:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了守護父親母親 我要打倒你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.02,0:16:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噴湧吧 我的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.79,0:16:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.39,0:16:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是…天龍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.15,0:16:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.31,0:16:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 天龍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.70,0:17:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是…我的新生聖衣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.31,0:17:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 不過是穿上了聖衣 有什麼好神氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.62,0:17:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是新生聖衣 防禦能力明顯提升了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.91,0:17:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.12,0:17:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光耀射擊（Flare Shoot）！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.05,0:17:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.05,0:18:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全身湧起力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.39,0:18:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖衣…正回應著我的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.77,0:18:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噴湧吧 我的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.14,0:18:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廬山升龍霸！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.53,0:18:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍峰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.44,0:18:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.74,0:18:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我記住
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.50,0:18:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次我一定會幹掉你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.01,0:19:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉睡的龍好像覺醒了啊 龍峰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.60,0:19:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親 您看到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.99,0:19:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在注視著你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.39,0:19:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.41,0:19:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你的話 即使沒有我的幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.92,0:19:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也一定能奮戰到底
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.37,0:19:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.62,0:19:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍峰！沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.88,0:19:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.12,0:19:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.40,0:19:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刻鬥士盯上你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.10,0:19:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放馬過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.05,0:19:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都不要大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.04,0:19:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你笑什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.90,0:19:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍峰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.19,0:19:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人沒有來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.45,0:19:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…已經打倒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.21,0:19:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.04,0:20:12.58,remark,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一級刻鬥士 泰坦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.92,0:20:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕拉斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.25,0:20:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.39,0:20:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我名為泰坦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.07,0:20:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是侍奉您 守護您之人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.14,0:20:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後 您無論有何事 都請吩咐我泰坦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.84,0:20:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 請多指教哦 泰坦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.66,0:20:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕拉斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.16,0:20:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.31,0:20:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親 母親
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.10,0:21:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從今往後也會繼續戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.60,0:21:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到迎來三人一起平靜生活的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.53,0:21:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好表現哦 龍峰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.89,0:21:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信同伴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.73,0:21:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話 前進之路自然會敞開
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.07,0:21:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 天龍座紫龍的兒子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.56,0:21:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我決一勝負吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.15,0:21:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…你還沒做過自我介紹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.85,0:21:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小朋友 你的名字是？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.45,0:21:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別叫我小朋友！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.76,0:21:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫昴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.15,0:21:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 我接下來打算去找榮斗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.62,0:21:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家回到聖域 跟其他的聖鬥士匯合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.54,0:21:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.58,0:21:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要小心 光牙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.21,0:21:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.41,0:21:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 榮斗我記得是…天狼座？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.49,0:21:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 那傢伙現在好像在故鄉日本
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.49,0:21:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.55,0:22:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想見見榮斗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.68,0:22:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天狼之聲在都市中迴響
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.60,0:22:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離開黑暗追尋光明的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.42,0:22:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要回到披掛聖衣戰鬥的道路上嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.39,0:22:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是握住話筒 銘刻心靈的呼喊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.50,0:22:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,榮斗 追尋夢之狼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.34,0:22:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賭上人生 向著月亮嗥叫吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.93,0:22:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 聖鬥士星矢Ω
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.13,0:22:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,響徹心靈！榮斗的嘶吼！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.69,0:22:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你曾感受到小宇宙的存在嗎